Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類一直在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與來自神秘遠方的敵人 － {\fnArial}Festum{\fnsimhei} 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你死就是我亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此毫無妥協的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護一些人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一些人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一個講述無休止的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.86,pic1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(551,425)\frz-20}（歡慶畢業）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉行了那一年的第二個「畢業」典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…今與諸位學長分別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人深感惆悵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們絕不會忘記諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請學長們一切珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿忘島上渡過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心祝願身體健康 工作順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謹表贈別之意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭賀諸位畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有學生會長氣勢的告別辭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 副會長幫我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 你這懶蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要和你分別了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空會回來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「畢業」成了定局之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有些不適應 對這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘快融入大人之中反而更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早點確定自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁還能活在義務教育世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如向喜歡的人告白之類的 什麼都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心存遺憾是最糟糕的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有留下遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,義務教育都沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就進入完全不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是龍宮島特有的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和劍司一如既往的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還賭劍司贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士賭哪邊贏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提劍司是13連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去可是很要好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和總士 他們倆小時候常在一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在一起玩是有原因的吧 相互之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事要低頭懇求身為副會長的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我養著牠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！帶牠一起走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 藏前 接下來的事拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長竟然先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道明天有休學典禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想說是去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他能撐著來就已經很辛苦了 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 那傢伙是個懶蟲也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們加油幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的 只是有些貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你還挺熱心腸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看你表情很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎沒跟其他人一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別老等著劍司那樣的人衝到面前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要主動和別人搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說你幫了我 說這話好像不大厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去遠見醫生那邊喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間也來作檢查？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡覺之前還好好的 今天卻不能上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是遺傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長得的病跟媽媽一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然和媽媽沒有血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很羡慕羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有位真心體貼你的好母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症狀穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,減少止疼藥的劑量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 無法再復原了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症狀也有可能完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說那個選拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 情況一定不會悲觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 聽說可以自願參加 鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最害怕一事無成就結束了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親去世已經兩年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨立生活有困難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島這麼小 總有人幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 我也不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間 不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢馬上就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:09:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 有個好朋友真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的好朋友一半以上都「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持上學 還當學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在我休假時 大家擅自決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 一上學就突然多了個頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這樣 不覺得討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像硬塞給你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒有忘記我 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們為我準備了容身之處 我應該報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算去學校 恐怕也沒有容身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍惜陪在你身邊的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長 真壁叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我馬上去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 只是來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心養病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 今天上午又舉行「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放暑假之前 舉行好幾次「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡是個荒僻的小島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸小時候的畢業典禮也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我「畢業」後會去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会陪在爸爸身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连带妈妈的份一直陪在您身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門重複發出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計700小時之內將得到明確應答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不能迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的核正在形成人格 若此時和敵人接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整座島都被奪取的可能性太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是只能將防禦系統降低到極限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們直接跟生駒談了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點將全部{\fnArial}Fafner{\r}相關兵器嚴密封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為將被敵人奪取後的打擊降到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能主動封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 僅此實在不能算是萬全之策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對此生駒所提出迴避危機的計劃 即是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若要實施 {\fnArial}TSX{\fnsimhei}的投入是大前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 難道要讓孩子們參與嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要掌控這個島的人們共同決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（暑假）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要打贏你 別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未前辈是学生会副会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会觉得很辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要面对在学校里带着狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还工作偷懒的学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能觉得很有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副会长的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是学生会长他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢……两方都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天要和朋友出去一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友約我去海邊玩 很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒讓我想起這島雖小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候卻也不愁找不到地方玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你約我來的 自己卻不下去游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的泳姿 就失去信心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你去看過遠見醫生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是有些不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微能明白這樣的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直和爸爸生活在一起 習慣照顧人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體也曬暖了 去游一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒想過讓別人照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果傷了你的心 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很開心 許久未曾這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能稍微拋開爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Al…vis…{\fnsimhei}必須…得去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去{\fnArial}Alvis…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士同學 令尊常去看我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 說是在公事上聽取一些建議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Plan…L
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner…Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}是為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嗎 你在那裡嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,識別限制編碼確認為第三級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TSX
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TS…X
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝賀你「畢業」 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的聲音一直在我腦海裡迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠學習({\fnArial}Memorizing{\fnsimhei})的知識\N是作為聲音來被認知的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到的是媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠學習？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小開始就被無意識灌輸的各種知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現今的世界形勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於島內部的{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及與敵人戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的人就算「畢業」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦知道 就無法回到平常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要選擇和大人們一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚為什麼沒有離開島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父親所設立的拯救島的L計劃啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對父親的事情一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親一定想讓我參加這個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會唸著{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 你還什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就一直都明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒跟你出去 爸爸就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵前辈...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 普库
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业去向决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假结束以后 离开岛和大人们一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真将陵前辈很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于工作什么的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的话 羽佐间也一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我离开了 这句话一定要记着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要選擇和父親相同的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您成全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的指令書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下終於可以報答給我容身之處的人們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业去向决定了 来打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了参加父亲的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才和校长已经谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 会直接和敌人战斗阿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前多少一样的计划我也听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果谁都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也... 那为什么你也要参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会藏在海里面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算就一直闭口不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去 不要再接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 選拔成員聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠自主催眠學習
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協同線路產生數值高的最適合者們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天起負責各位訓練的日野惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出作戰的人可隨時向我提出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始說明{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在敵人正逐漸察覺此島的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃正是為了避免之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}即指{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的左翼 {\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}區域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其從島上分離開 成為{\fnArial}L Boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}能夠在超越敵人探知能力的深海中前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到島的防禦圈外上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引敵人 按既定航線繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為期兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓其誤以為{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}就是龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須持續迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這艘{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}是自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己身在何處也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這將是極其嚴苛的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出的人請提出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼立即開始訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}的第一大特徵 即無需操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵從催眠學習獲得的知識 和{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受精神的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是訓練用的虛擬現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.43,0:24:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.22,0:24:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跑 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸毫無困難
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.37,0:24:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 這不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.21,0:24:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.71,0:24:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二大特徵 即各機內置系統間的交叉({\fnArial}Crossing{\fnsimhei})
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.17,0:24:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共享思考 防止被敵人讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.50,0:25:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要接受同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.21,0:25:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.82,0:25:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.71,0:25:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 請換其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.60,0:25:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了取得平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是他 你馬上就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.68,0:25:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 你害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.19,0:25:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是僚的感覺？你在享受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.99,0:25:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘上這個 我也能游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.38,0:25:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制時間到 請離開駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.65,0:25:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}的第三大特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.80,0:25:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即駕駛員會被同化現象所侵擾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.98,0:25:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐次數越多 肉體越容易發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.68,0:25:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最壞情況下可能危及生命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.44,0:25:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退出吧 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.10,0:26:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.09,0:26:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了爸爸一定要讓計劃成功
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.58,0:26:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是一開始就不想活著回去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.86,0:26:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如退出算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.14,0:26:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選拔成員共8人 無人退出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.99,0:26:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}共4架 每架由兩人交替駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.97,0:26:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次戰鬥時間15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.07,0:26:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人交替 各戰鬥450秒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.60,0:26:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷重複的戰鬥訓練 以及敵人的確認
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.46,0:26:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矽狀生命體 － {\fnArial}Festum {\fnsimhei}即敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.31,0:26:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有統一的思考 能適應任何環境
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.66,0:26:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但未曾在海中發現過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據推測是其若與海中結晶物同化
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.48,0:26:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會成為不規則塊狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.64,0:26:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是「畢業」的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.54,0:26:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而對我來說 還有一項重要的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.73,0:27:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 普庫 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我給的 它從不吃任何食物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.68,0:27:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定察覺到會被丟下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.87,0:27:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帶狗一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.91,0:27:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為飼主 要負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.09,0:27:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條狗是從前媽媽帶回來 讓我當成朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.34,0:27:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法去上學時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.16,0:27:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有它在身邊 我就不會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.19,0:27:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.89,0:27:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知有毒還去吃的對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.93,0:27:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.75,0:28:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.63,0:28:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.87,0:28:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖等著學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.10,0:28:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為獎勵 學長們的慰問品分你一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的新型{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.03,0:28:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月後計劃完畢之前 應該趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們沒事 就能來迎接我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.78,0:28:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.55,0:28:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長 它好像肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.40,0:28:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.12,0:28:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這是隨身物品 可能有點重
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.64,0:28:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.44,0:28:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.39,0:28:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我會把它當成學長好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.26,0:28:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.36,0:28:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 完成最後一項準備時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:28:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何想起了祐未的話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就覺得回不去的人 應該退出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.55,0:29:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 多半祐未是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.39,0:29:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝鏡面 維持{\fnArial}ROM{\fnsimhei}模式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.46,0:29:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接續區域 全部隔離壁以緊急模式封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.40,0:29:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全隔離壁封鎖確認
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開啟注水閥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.78,0:29:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接續區域 確認注水
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.24,0:29:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}艦橋呼叫{\fnArial}CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.48,0:29:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序鏈接無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.29,0:29:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注水完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.42,0:29:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat {\fnsimhei}出發準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.38,0:29:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}區域分離準備 全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.12,0:29:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分離
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.51,0:29:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}控制程序開始運行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駛向波盾圈外
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.33,0:29:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月後再會
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝他們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.38,0:29:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二步驟啟動 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.51,0:29:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.14,0:30:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離計劃結束的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.28,0:30:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9月2號 {\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.56,0:30:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}即{\fnArial}Left {\fnsimhei}左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也含有離去的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.97,0:30:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如這個詞所說 我們離開了島
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.72,0:30:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發後第3天 我們的小島上浮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.37,0:30:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起 這裡就是龍宮島了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.92,0:30:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人實體化 是{\fnArial}Sphinx {\fnsimhei}型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.15,0:30:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以普通武器牽制 {\fnArial}Fafner {\fnsimhei}準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.97,0:30:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}能量傳輸線連接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.36,0:30:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}7至8號
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.83,0:30:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Brunhild{\fnsimhei}系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.27,0:30:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}數據線確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.22,0:30:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}搭乘輸入優先
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.28,0:30:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}速度控制
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.41,0:30:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}負極數據輸入中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.66,0:30:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}誤差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}傳感器開放
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}各機正常
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.77,0:30:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}封鎖解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.29,0:30:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Niebelungen{\fnsimhei}系統開啟確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.05,0:30:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統接續完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.39,0:30:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}接續桿連接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:30:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}艙門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.93,0:30:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}啟動升降架接續
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}上升
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.79,0:31:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}潮流數據 環境數據及氣象數據輸入完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.75,0:31:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到的敵人 超乎想像的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.34,0:31:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.38,0:31:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.29,0:32:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 打倒敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.93,0:32:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次打倒敵人 大家深受鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.55,0:32:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試圖用興奮壓抑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.11,0:32:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有歸路了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.31,0:32:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 为什么我的饭你会吃掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.07,0:32:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是被抛弃后一个人呢 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.95,0:32:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里曾是fafner的启动事件失败后 消灭后产生的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:33:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.42,0:33:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步走错的话 就会葬身海里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.80,0:33:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样也要做么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.15,0:33:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵前辈的事情想起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种的事 害怕什么的早就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.39,0:33:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想像的小
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.19,0:33:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒有內置{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.98,0:33:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.47,0:33:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.12,0:33:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.47,0:33:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markeins {\fnsimhei}終止啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.72,0:33:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}eins:{\fnsimhei}德語「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.40,0:33:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然對與{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}一體化來說 是致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.16,0:33:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次 請讓我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.75,0:33:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.85,0:33:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.23,0:34:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員喪失意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.49,0:34:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3號機的駕駛員來這邊 交換
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩天一次 敵人不斷來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.81,0:34:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後有人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.27,0:34:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第6次戰鬥時 那件事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.87,0:34:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是乘坐{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.84,0:34:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的肉體越會結晶化
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.38,0:34:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.27,0:34:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第8次戰鬥時 又有一人倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.20,0:34:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.72,0:35:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是敵人 而是本應是武器的{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.42,0:35:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為減少駕駛員的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.23,0:35:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該把戰鬥時間從15分鐘縮短為10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.76,0:35:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣出擊次數就會增大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊時 牽制敵人的彈藥不足
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.98,0:35:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反需要增加戰鬥時間
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.99,0:35:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從父親口中聽說過這個計劃的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.41,0:35:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.70,0:35:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃結束時的逃生方法是什麼 連我也未被告知
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便沒有逃生方法 我也早有心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…父親他 絕不會把我們當成犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未的父親並不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.89,0:35:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能提出這麼快就無法戰鬥的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.32,0:35:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該縮短戰鬥時間到10分鐘 減少駕駛員的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.58,0:36:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與根據現狀的判斷相比 你更相信計劃立案者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.77,0:36:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未的父親自己也打算參加
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.95,0:36:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為他想活著回島
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.19,0:36:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說重病纏身時日無多的人還打算生還嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.84,0:36:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.52,0:36:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知從何時起 我就變得如此相信
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.46,0:36:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.03,0:36:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得 如果自己病情嚴重惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.07,0:36:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會比現在更想活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.56,0:36:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人在放哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.70,0:36:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.07,0:36:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.31,0:36:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.82,0:36:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.62,0:36:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.05,0:36:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太擔心的話 你又要發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.74,0:36:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候被人提起自己的身體 有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.58,0:36:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天謝謝你 替我父親辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.95,0:37:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.99,0:37:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是…對不起 你父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.12,0:37:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為無法活著回去也無所謂的 是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.57,0:37:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 你一直想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.74,0:37:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你和爸爸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.15,0:37:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯有你 我不想失去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.03,0:37:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快到會議室來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.92,0:37:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.09,0:37:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封閉的區域自動開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.66,0:37:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給我們的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.65,0:37:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.23,0:37:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人會讀取我們的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.73,0:37:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判斷武器的能力而進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.52,0:37:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要騙過敵人先得騙過自己 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.17,0:37:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.17,0:37:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在一定時期後 就會提供一些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.31,0:38:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最後打開的…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.35,0:38:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是逃生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.30,0:38:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 勿庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.82,0:38:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸果然了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.30,0:38:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要的一定是生存之地 而不是葬身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.22,0:38:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.42,0:38:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員另選其他人擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.07,0:38:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來操縱{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.21,0:38:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您叫我不親臨陣前 反而把同伴送去戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.21,0:38:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這比較適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.72,0:38:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親認為這次計劃能有多少人生還
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.37,0:38:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生駒提出的生存率極低
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.42,0:38:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您依然批准了計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.75,0:38:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要我做同樣的事 為了保護島而付出犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.48,0:38:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生駒想盡力生存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.59,0:39:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我批准了計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.16,0:39:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我堅信他們能夠全部生還
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.97,0:39:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在殘酷的境遇中掙扎求生者的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.34,0:39:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能夠背負嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.98,0:39:23.68,pic2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(473,201)}（活下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.99,0:39:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥越來越激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.26,0:39:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.31,0:40:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.73,0:40:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅有的4架{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}中 有一架喪失了機能
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.09,0:40:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的數量再次減少
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.28,0:40:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚能戰鬥的人身上 也出現了同化現象的早期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.60,0:40:33.11,pic3,NTP,0,0,0,,（希望早日結束）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.43,0:40:34.11,pic4,NTP,0,0,0,,（快點！快點！快點！我想回家！）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.29,0:40:35.01,pic5,NTP,0,0,0,,（爸爸 媽媽）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.15,0:40:35.78,pic6,NTP,0,0,0,,（我們在這裡）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.40,0:40:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 終於駕駛員中也開始出現犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.20,0:40:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸弘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.13,0:41:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是同化現象的末期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.38,0:41:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴們 一個接一個 在我們眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.09,0:41:20.55,pic7,NTP,0,0,0,,（反正大家最後都要死）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.72,0:41:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 為什麼寫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.48,0:41:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.50,0:41:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.42,0:41:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再逼他了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.49,0:41:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人的心中都充滿了恐懼 憤怒和悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.23,0:41:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩下兩周
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.98,0:41:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我們再度失去了{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.92,0:42:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化現象的早期症狀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.17,0:42:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.41,0:42:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧這個 才不會被其他人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在第三次啟動時成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.48,0:42:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣身體就出現異變 真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.43,0:42:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長他們還要更加辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.85,0:42:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一派和平
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.62,0:42:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想把學長們的事告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.66,0:42:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會讓學長們的戰鬥變得毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.58,0:42:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人做出犧牲 卻只有我們待在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.81,0:42:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.00,0:42:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能祈求這是正確的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.89,0:42:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說皆城已經決定操縱系統了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.73,0:42:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.11,0:42:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倖存下來的有兩架{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.25,0:42:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3名駕駛員和8位成人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.06,0:43:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.31,0:43:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡竟然有通道
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.50,0:43:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是逃生方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.86,0:43:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.79,0:43:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.73,0:43:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.66,0:43:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 那艘潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.49,0:43:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠搭乘40人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.41,0:43:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸認為所有人都能生還
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.56,0:43:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.04,0:43:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經活到現在了 一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.56,0:43:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}第9至第17區域注水開始
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.28,0:43:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}第1第2第3隔離壁開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.71,0:43:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}逃生程序確認
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.42,0:43:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fnsimhei}啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.69,0:43:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想與{\fnArial}Festum{\fnsimhei}同歸於盡 銷毀這個島嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.81,0:43:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.27,0:43:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.56,0:44:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fnsimhei}釋放還有5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.59,0:44:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.55,0:44:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.50,0:44:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.37,0:44:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.24,0:44:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦圈內有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.15,0:44:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潛水艇和{\fnArial}Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.00,0:44:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備出擊 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.21,0:44:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner·Markzwei {\fnsimhei}出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.75,0:44:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}zwei:{\fnsimhei}德語「2」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.73,0:44:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間正面出現{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.62,0:44:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短魚雷及導彈戰準備
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.69,0:44:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,252度也出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.14,0:44:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.13,0:45:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.94,0:45:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後方約20公里處
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.10,0:45:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.09,0:45:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們幾時能下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.13,0:45:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛水艇消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.53,0:45:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.32,0:45:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島應該在這個方向 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.83,0:45:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.81,0:45:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.92,0:45:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經知道龍宮島在這前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.82,0:45:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.48,0:45:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能百分之百確定 就不能這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.47,0:45:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.84,0:45:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去 回島上去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.22,0:45:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況已經變了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.68,0:45:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能讓大家的戰鬥失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.37,0:45:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 在有人來迎接我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.42,0:45:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Titan-model{\fnsimhei}開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.79,0:45:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠離島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.84,0:46:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 停住{\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.20,0:46:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能發生了最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.81,0:46:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.30,0:46:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓整座島置身險境 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fnsimhei}停止前進
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.34,0:46:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 不去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.97,0:46:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待機 {\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.59,0:46:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況變了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.80,0:46:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 不是要去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.77,0:46:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.29,0:46:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待機！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.81,0:46:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我絕不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.26,0:46:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖定{\fnArial}Markzwei{\fnsimhei}的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.06,0:46:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你讓我去 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.96,0:46:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城 聽得見吧 為什麼不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.53,0:46:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.67,0:46:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.06,0:46:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}CDC {\fnsimhei}那邊是有著實戰經驗的機體和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.43,0:46:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能回收那些數據
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.28,0:47:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的戰力將大幅提升
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.95,0:47:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也更能抵抗敵人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.84,0:47:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.87,0:47:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲得與敵人戰鬥力量的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.87,0:47:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算眼睜睜地錯過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.96,0:47:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}是做什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.18,0:47:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.42,0:47:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能讓{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}離開防禦圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.31,0:47:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.11,0:47:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fnsimhei}重整機體
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.77,0:47:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後全力追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.73,0:47:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.38,0:47:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計測目標週邊所有振動
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.71,0:47:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.34,0:47:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能得到答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.89,0:47:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潮流的數據收集到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.10,0:47:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這裡運氣好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.14,0:47:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少殘骸能回到島上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.01,0:47:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.37,0:47:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.89,0:48:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 制止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.86,0:48:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.01,0:48:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.80,0:48:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.24,0:48:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我一直喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.59,0:48:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 從很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.54,0:48:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.49,0:48:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時 已經超越了那種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.76,0:48:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.82,0:48:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.93,0:48:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的人們會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.49,0:48:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.85,0:48:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸會稱讚我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.50,0:49:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪？下在海底？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.56,0:49:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.56,0:49:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}海雪︰海底浮游生物組成的絮狀物，看起來像雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.47,0:49:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在稱讚我們呢 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.53,0:49:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.20,0:49:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在陪在我身邊的是你 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.23,0:49:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.84,0:49:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.69,0:49:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.13,0:49:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像還有更多更深的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.26,0:49:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你陪在身邊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.20,0:50:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.66,0:50:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.36,0:50:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了嗎 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.89,0:50:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.59,0:50:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.22,0:50:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你們以前從未到過海中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.36,0:50:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由於無法代謝而結晶化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.34,0:51:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代謝…就是使身體重生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.08,0:51:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也掌握了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.99,0:51:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 才擁有了生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.03,0:51:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fenrir{\fnsimhei}釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.20,0:51:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認信源地
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.92,0:51:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判斷為海底有人啟動了{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.77,0:51:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.57,0:51:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心機體被敵人同化
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.42,0:51:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明海底也存在{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.45,0:51:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給我們的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.67,0:51:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Markzwei 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.27,0:51:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡已經 沒有任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.69,0:52:04.65,pic8,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,276)\fad(2000,2000)}四\N個\N月\N後
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.60,0:52:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是第一波盾的潮流感應器探查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.84,0:52:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著珍貴的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.59,0:52:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.68,0:52:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 分析了潮流後才啟動的{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.03,0:52:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是保持鎮靜直到最後的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.55,0:52:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰駕駛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.06,0:52:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據調查 似乎只留下了音頻記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.38,0:52:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 普庫 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.92,0:52:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.97,0:52:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.00,0:53:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.89,0:53:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普庫
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.80,0:53:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 待在這裡的是將陵學長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.44,0:53:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是陪伴祐未學姐直到最後的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.44,0:54:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起 一定是去了將陵學長身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.07,0:54:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了 想把它送回龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.87,0:54:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門的反應顯示著徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.47,0:54:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計很快將輪到{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}迎擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.53,0:54:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平僅僅維持了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.00,0:54:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長他們的戰鬥 只有這點意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.47,0:54:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直享受著別人贏來並讓給的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.37,0:54:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那和平只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.66,0:54:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會感謝其價值
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.98,0:54:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.02,0:54:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待與你並肩作戰的時刻到來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.63,0:55:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 我們繼承了和平與戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.52,0:55:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想要活下去的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.88,0:55:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及在前線戰鬥者的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.12,0:55:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能否全部承受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.58,0:55:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不斷重複問著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.61,0:55:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案 就在今後的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.19,0:52:28.72,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どれくらい時間があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.50,0:52:33.38,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心は繋がるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.62,0:52:40.16,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どこか寂しげな笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.52,0:52:44.62,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,癒せたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.24,0:52:52.65,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,近すぎて気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.46,0:52:57.81,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,一番大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.42,0:53:04.19,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,傍に居てくれるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.50,0:53:09.86,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,幸せを感じられる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.06,0:53:12.94,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しみの夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.01,0:53:15.94,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,喜びの朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.01,0:53:21.97,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしを見守ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.48,0:53:28.13,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ一言「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.47,0:53:33.46,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,伝えられないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.95,0:53:36.86,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.99,0:53:39.82,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.03,0:53:45.44,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.54,0:53:52.44,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.68,0:54:01.64,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.19,0:54:16.65,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,静けさにふと窓の外
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.51,0:54:21.42,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,雪が舞い降りている
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.51,0:54:27.80,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,真白に染まる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.56,0:54:33.78,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの音に寄り添う
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.06,0:54:36.86,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.00,0:54:39.93,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.10,0:54:45.45,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.54,0:54:52.41,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.80,0:55:02.97,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.19,0:52:28.72,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要經過多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.50,0:52:33.38,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,心才能相映
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.62,0:52:40.16,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,些許寂寞的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.52,0:52:44.62,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,多想將其治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.24,0:52:52.65,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,太過靠近而未曾察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.46,0:52:57.81,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.42,0:53:04.19,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,只是陪在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.50,0:53:09.86,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.06,0:53:12.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.01,0:53:15.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悅的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.01,0:53:21.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,都為我守候
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.48,0:53:28.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,連一句感謝的話語
