Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.51,0:54:27.80,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,在純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.56,0:54:33.78,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,依偎著你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.06,0:54:36.86,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.00,0:54:39.93,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,還有些膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.10,0:54:45.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,如今在你懷中
